                                                                           \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Ways Outlook on Mac is better than Windows\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/reasons-outlook-on-mac-is-better-than-windows.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/how-to-set-out-of-office-in-outlook/\" title=\"How to set out of office status in Outlook\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tHow to set out of office status in Outlook\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThere\u0026#39;s nothing fun about individually canceling every single meeting you\u0026#39;re about to miss\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\t\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-block-emails-in-microsoft-outlook\"\u003e\n                        How to block emails in Microsoft Outlook\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor this example, we used Outlook on a Windows PC with an active Microsoft 365 subscription to block emails with the following steps. However, the same feature is available on Outlook for iOS and Android with just a slightly different method (which we will cover below).\u003c/p\u003e        \u003col\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Launch \u003cstrong\u003eOutlook\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Go to the \u003cstrong\u003eHome\u003c/strong\u003e tab.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Click the \u003cstrong\u003eJunk Mail \u003c/strong\u003eicon, then select \u003cstrong\u003eJunk E-mail Options\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                            