rcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"3018\" height=\"1700\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Junk Mail option in Microsoft Outlook on Windows\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-junk-email-options.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Click on the \u003cstrong\u003eBlocked Senders\u003c/strong\u003e tab to enter the email addresses you want blocked.\n                                            \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"3024\" height=\"1794\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Using the Blocked Senders window in Microsoft Outlook on Windows\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-senders.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Click\u003cstrong\u003e OK\u003c/strong\u003e and confirm.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-quickly-block-an-email-in-microsoft-outlook\"\u003e\n                        How to quickly block an email in Microsoft Outlook\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you prefer to quickly block an email as you sort through your inbox, here’s how to do so.\u003c/p\u003e        \u003col\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Launch \u003cstrong\u003eOutlook\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Click on the unwelcome email in your inbox.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Go to the \u003cstrong\u003eHome \u003c/strong\u003etab, then click the \u003cstrong\u003eJunk icon\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eBlock Sender\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                                            \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Blocking a sender in Microsoft Outlook on Windows\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/microsoft-outlook-block-sender-2.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-block-emails-in-microsoft-outlook-for-ios-and-android\"\u003e\n                        How to block emails in Microsoft Outlook for iOS and Android\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs mentioned, you can block emails with the Outlook app available on \u003ca href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/microsoft-outlook/id951937596\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eiOS\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.microsoft.office.outlook\u0026amp;hl=en_GB\u0026amp;pli=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAndroid\u003c/a\u003e. It’s a straightforward process that only takes a couple of steps.\u003c/p\u003e        \u003col\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Launch \u003cstrong\u003eOutlook\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Find the unwanted email in your inbox.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Once found,\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003etap\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003eon the \u003cstrong\u003ethree dots\u003c/strong\u003e shown on the top-right of the email, then select \u003cstrong\u003eReport Junk\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Tap on \u003cstrong\u003eBlock Sender \u003c/strong\u003eand confirm it.\n                                            \n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThat’s all you need to do. Managing emails can be a hassle, and it doesn\u0026#39;t help when you receive emails that aren’t even relevant to you. If you follow these steps, you’ll never see these unwanted emails again.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"feel-like-it-rsquo-s-time-to-switch-mail-apps\"\u003e\n                        Feel like it’s time to switch mail apps?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMicrosoft Outlook isn’t the only mail app on Windows that allows you to manage your inbox and block unwanted emails. There are some fantastic alternatives out there that might better suit your workflow. If you’re curious about other apps that can help manage your inbox, take a look at our helpful guide of \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/these-are-the-best-mail-app-alternatives-for-your-windows-pc/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efive other mail apps\u003c/a\u003e you can use right now on your Windows PC.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n